## 📋 **النص بالإنجليزي (للـ Privacy Policy):**

```markdown
## Battery Optimization Permission

### Why We Need This Permission
Our app is a prayer times reminder service that requires exemption from
battery optimization to function correctly. This permission ensures that:

- Prayer call (Adhan) notifications are delivered at the exact prayer times
- Notifications work reliably even when your device is in sleep/Doze mode
- The app can run background tasks to schedule prayer reminders accurately

### How We Use This Permission
- **Sole Purpose:** To deliver timely and accurate Islamic prayer time notifications
- **No Abuse:** We do NOT use this permission for advertising, tracking, or
  any purpose other than prayer reminders
- **User Control:** This permission is optional. You can choose to decline it,
  but prayer notifications may be delayed or missed

### When We Request This Permission
The app will prompt you to disable battery optimization when:
- You first open the prayer times screen
- You manually check the battery settings via the app icon

You can always change this setting later through your device's Settings >
Apps > [App Name] > Battery > Unrestricted.

### Compliance
This permission usage complies with Google Play's policies for alarm clock
and reminder applications, as outlined in the Android documentation for
acceptable use cases of battery optimization exemptions.

---

Last Updated: [ضع تاريخ اليوم]
```

